{
  "description": "A young boy stands with his back to the viewer on a paved plaza. The plaza is constructed of dark gray rectangular tiles bordered by light gray lines. His long shadow stretches out in front of him, created by warm afternoon light. Behind him, a low beige wall forms a backdrop, and a few dark rectangular objects (possibly benches or planters) are placed against it. Beyond the wall, a hillside covered with green and yellow trees rises, and a light-colored building is partially visible at the top of the hill. The sky is a mix of light blue and yellow from the setting sun, with some wispy clouds. The scene conveys a sense of peaceful solitude and quiet contemplation.",
